{"tid":1205102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防處屬員 有責任保護市民","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:47:34.000Z","uid":515,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d822834d54140d86bf00f442e3851c86b2b0229c","tid":1205102,"uid":515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"在火警或<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其他災難</strong></span>發生時保護人命及財產；<br />\n用以下方法<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>協助任何看似需要</strong></span>迅速或立即接受醫療護理的人 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>確保該人的安全</strong></span>；<br />\n(ii)令該人復甦或維持其生命；<br />\n(iii)減少其痛苦或困擾；<br />\n<br />\n職責之一 責無旁貸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/10/3df78d7b166d451b90fbe9400490c304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F10%2F3df78d7b166d451b90fbe9400490c304.jpg&h=5c5e884e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20171002-photo-catalan-referendum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20171002-photo-catalan-referendum%2F&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=20607cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20171002-photo-catalan-referendum/</a>"},{"pid":"55b864f320af61a6029fc34872543285d3be5c53","tid":1205102,"uid":4739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBxbby0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBxbby0.png&h=103606af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c0120a5085f